ating officer from may  to may  mr mollins was executive vice president from november  to january  he also served as vice president and chief operating officer from  to  and as vice president from  to  mr mollins joined reliance in  as division manager of the former santa clara division following ten years with certain of our competitors in various sales and sales management positions mr mollins has spent his entire career in the metals service center industry and has been exposed to every operational area of the business as our president and chief executive officer he has extensive industry expertise and has developed extensive contacts in the metals service center industry and with mills and other suppliers mr mollins evaluates potential acquisitions and opportunities to expand our business and has the skills and experience necessary to supervise the daytoday operations of the company and to guide its strategy mr mollins is actively involved in the integration of new acquisitions into the companys culture source reliance steel  aluminum co on    sign up for equilar atlas and view gregg j mollinss full profile by accessing equilar atlas you can view bios network salary and wealth events of industryleading executives like gregg j mollins more specifically youll be able to identify corporate executives in gregg j mollinss network and community follow changes in gregg j mollinss employment and moneyinmotion connect with gregg j mollins through your network of conections view full profile   search for over  executive profiles bio example gregg j mollins gregg j mollinss connections  sign up now to view gregg j mollinss  connections » douglas m hayes board member reliance steel  aluminum co douglas w stotlar board member aecom mark v kaminski lead director reliance steel  aluminum co david h hannah board member reliance steel  aluminum co william i rumer former board member reliance steel  aluminum co andrew g sharkey board member reliance steel  aluminum co robert heni