 he was appointed president and chief operating officer mr mollins has also served on the companys board of directors since   i congratulate gregg on his welldeserved appointment as reliances chief executive officer said mr hannah since joining reliance in  gregg has held various positions of increasing responsibility and demonstrated business savvy and excellent judgment and leadership in each role his unique abilities and talents have earned him the respect of our customers suppliers shareholders and employees alike todays announcement is the culmination of a deliberate succession planning process developed in conjunction with our board and i am extremely confident that gregg is the right person to lead reliance going forward i am pleased to pass the ceo title to him and look forward to maintaining an active role as executive chairman of the board   mr mollins commented i am honored by the opportunity to serve as reliances next ceo and to continue our track record of success as the premier metals service center company in north america i look forward to continuing to work with our incredibly talented team at reliance to build upon our accomplishments and help the company execute our strategy and deliver more industry leading results reliance also announced several other promotions in connection with its management succession plan each to take effect concurrently with mr mollins promotion on may    karla r lewis reliances executive vice president and chief financial officer since  will be promoted to senior executive vice president and cfo and will continue to lead the companys overall financial operations ms lewis who has been with reliance since  oversees reliances accounting financial planning capital allocation and investor relations activities william k sales jr will be promoted to the office of executive vice president operations  mr sales has served as senior vice president of operations since  and oversees the companys nonferrous operations including the aerospace semiconductor and electronics industries  james d hoffman will also be promoted to the office of executive vice president operations mr hoffman has served as the companys senior vice president of operations since  and oversees the companys carbon steel and alloy operations including the energy auto and nonresidential construction industries in light of mr mollins promotion and to ensure appropriate reassignment of some of mr mollins current operations management duties effective april   michael p shanley currently president of liebovich brothers inc a whollyowned subsidiary of reliance will assume the title of senior vice president operations   each of mr sales mr hoffman and stephen p koch senior vice president operations since  will continue to report to mr mollins mrs lewis and mr shanley will also report to mr mollins in closing mr hannah said as we recently celebrated our th corporate anniversary at reliance and our th year as an nyselisted company we are very pleased to announce these promotions which we believe will ensure that reliance will continue into the future as the great company it has become in its first  years about reliance steel  aluminum co reliance steel  aluminum co headquartered in los angeles california is the largest metals service center company in north america through a network of more than  locations in  states and twelve countries outside of the united states the company provides valueadded metals processing services and distributes a full line of over  metal products to more than  customers in a broad range of industries reliance steel  aluminum cos press releases and additional information are available on the companys web site at wwwrsaccom contact  brenda miyamoto investor relations   investorrsaccom or addo communications   logo  httpphotosprnewswirecomprnh   source reliance steel  aluminum co related links wwwrsaccom view table fullscreen view table fullscreen journalists and bloggers the news you need when you need it joi